OL,3,CChild 'unnecessarily restrained' after
OL,4,Ctrust failed to monitor use of seating
OL,6,FThe child's mother also said the lap
OL,7,Fbelt on the chair was too tight.
OL,9,FThe report said when she raised this
OL,10,Fwith the trust she was told the chair
OL,11,Fwas also used by others in the school,
OL,12,Fand that her son could use another
OL,13,Fchair if she wished.
OL,15,FThe ombudsman said this was a highly
OL,16,Fspecialist chair for a child who has
OL,17,Fvery limited mobility.
OL,19,FThe report said it was more
OL,20,Frestrictive and had foot straps, a lap
OL,21,Fstrap, and a wheeled base.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
