OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Western Trust
OL,7,Fsaid: "The trust will be contacting
OL,8,Fthe service user and their family to
OL,9,Foffer a sincere apology.
OL,11,F"We have accepted the findings and
OL,12,Flearning within the ombudsman's report
OL,13,Fand an action plan has been developed
OL,14,Fto take the recommendations and
OL,15,Flearning forward."
